2015;;The Kind Words;;Canadian;;Shemi Zarhin;;Rotem Zissman-Cohen;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Kind_Words;;After the death of their mother, three Jewish Israeli siblings discover the man who raised them might not be their biological father. They plan to visit their aunt in France to learn the truth, but she evades their questions. Later, they find out the man they were looking is an Algerian, Maurice Leon, but he himself doesn't reveal who he his or his religion.